VICTOR AKANDE, JOE AGBRO, DUPE AYINLA-OLASUNKANMI, OLAITAN GANIU TERRA Kulture Arena in collaboration with Oba_X and Moet Hennessy  will light  up Lagos with a costume and concept party tagged, A Lagos Halloween. The party is slated for 9pm on Thursday, October 31 at the Terra Kulture Arena, Victoria Island, Lagos. In a statement , Oba_X said that the event will feature a line-up of popular artistes, Nollywood actors, DJs and fashion icons among others. He described ‘A Lagos Halloween’ as a costume party where everyone can be himself or pretend to be someone else for a whole night. “Halloween also known as All Hallows’ Eve, or All Saints’ Eve, is a celebration observed in several countries on October 31, the eve of the Western Christian feast of All Hallows’ Day”, he said. He also said that the best five costumes will win cash prizes.